creator: Micro Tech Medical(Hangzhou)Co.,LTD.
descriptionHtml:
The AiDEX App can be used with the AiDEX Continuous Glucose Monitoring System. The AiDEX App allows you to monitor your glucose with your phone. You could calibrate your glucose value after 6 hour your Sensor being inserted successfully. The AiDEX App is compatible with 7/10/14 days Sensors.
You can use the AiDEX App to:
•Check your glucose value every 5 mintutes, instead of a routine fingerstick.*
•View your current glucose reading, trend arrow, and history.
•Add notes to track your food, insulin use,medicine and exercise.
•See glucose reports, including your Ambulatory Glucose Profile.
•Connect to healthcare professionals with Pancares.**

*Fingersticks are required if your glucose alarms and readings do not match symptoms.
**For a list of compatible devices, please visit http://www.microtechmd.com/en/support/More-support
